      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "We believe that true equity means actively dismantling systemic barriers, not just making small tweaks. Our commitment to DEI is a strategic business choice that drives innovation and builds a community rooted in mutual respect.\n\nHere are three caption options for your Instagram post:\n\n**Option 1: Focus on Action**\n\"Equity isn't a checkbox; it's a daily practice. We're committed to creating a space where every voice matters and every customer feels seen. Let's build a community defined by genuine inclusion. 🌱☕️ #DEI #CoffeeCommunity #Inclusion\"\n\n**Option 2: Focus on Culture**\n\"Great coffee starts with great people. We are dedicated to fostering an environment where diversity thrives and everyone belongs. Join us in making a difference, one cup at a time. ☕️✨ #DiversityMatters #SmallBusiness #InclusiveCulture\"\n\n**Option 3: Short & Punchy**\n\"True equity means listening to everyone. We're here to create a welcoming space for all backgrounds and perspectives. Let's make a difference together. 🌍💼 #DEI #CoffeeShop #CommunityFirst\"",
