      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for these. i noticed in your intro you mentioned \"dismantling systemic barriers.\" that sounds a bit intense for a coffee shop lol. can you give me some options that are a bit more neutral/business-focused? i dont want to alienate customers who might have different political views on DEI.",
